@startuml sequence_citations
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask - Citations

participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "POST /api/ask" as API
participant "IChatClient" as CC

... streaming tokens (slice 11) ...
CC --> API: end
API --> UI: event: citations\ndata: [c1, c2, c3]
UI -> UI: append mini-cards to last assistant message
API --> UI: event: done

actor User
User -> UI: tap citation card
UI -> UI: router.navigate(/contacts/:id)

@enduml
